item.title: argh
item.description: today I am tired. I have been working all day an I just don’t feel well about it. like I should have slept or something. it is weird. I mean I did get up a bit late.. but I feel so “walking dead-ish” - ugh. whatever. I will wake up right nowlast night I got an email from riply’s believe it or not about our friend rusty. they simply can’t believe it and wondered the origin of the video.
